Homework 6: Textures

Colin O'Connell
CSCI4229 Fall 2018

Displays 2 chairs and a bench with different wood textures and shades. Includes a light revolving around the scene that affects the look of the chairs and bench.

Key bindings
  l          Toggles lighting
  t          Toggles texture mode
  a/s        Decrease/increase ambient light
  d/f        Decrease/increase diffuse light
  g/h        Decrease/increase specular light
  j/k        Decrease/increase emitted light
  z/x        Decrease/increase shininess
  m          Toggles light movement
  [/]         Lower/rise light
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
  
Time to complete assignment: 5 hours